@startuml
title 受理闭环用例图（当前实现）

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "客户端/前端" as Client
actor "运维/开发者" as Ops

rectangle "Ingest Acceptance Closure" {
  usecase "上传文档并受理\nPOST /api/v1/documents/upload" as UC_Accept
  usecase "查询文档当前状态\nGET /api/v1/documents/{documentId}/status" as UC_Status
  usecase "状态查询未命中\n返回 404" as UC_StatusNotFound
  usecase "参数非法/空文件\n返回 400" as UC_BadRequest
}

Client --> UC_Accept
Client --> UC_Status
Ops --> UC_Status

UC_StatusNotFound ..> UC_Status : <<extend>>
UC_BadRequest ..> UC_Accept : <<extend>>

note right of UC_Accept
  用例目标：
  1) 校验上传参数并计算 fileHash
  2) 按 kbId + fileHash 幂等受理
  3) 新资产落库为 UPLOADED
  4) 保存源文件（幂等写入）
  5) 对外返回 ACCEPTED
end note

note right of UC_Status
  用例目标：
  1) 按 documentId 查询当前状态
  2) 返回 UPLOADED/INGESTING/INDEXED/FAILED
  3) 未命中返回 404
end note

@enduml
